e confessional in modern Catholic faith \t\r\n\t\t\t\t  <span id=\"dna-comment-count___CPS__26549102\" class=\"gvl3-icon gvl3-icon-comment comment-count\"></span></p>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<hr />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t<li class=\"medium-image\">\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\" feature-header\">\r\n\t<a class=\"story\" rel=\"published-1392973359583\" href=\"/religion/0/26081279\"><img src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/72833000/jpg/_72833206_cardinalpic-gettyimages.jpg\" alt=\"Cardinals\" />Cardinals in the Church</a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</h3>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>BBC Religion and Ethics examines the role  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t  <span id=\"dna-comment-count___CPS__26081279\" class=\"gvl3-icon gvl3-icon-comment comment-count\"></span></p>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<hr />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\r\n\t \r\n\t\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n  \t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t<!-- Non specific version -->\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t<li class=\"no-image\">\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\" feature-header\">\r\n\t<a class=\"story\" rel=\"published-1345555727657\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/religion/religions/\">Religion A-Z</a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</h3>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Find out more about the world&#039;s different religions \t\r\n\t\t\t\t  <span id=\"dna-comment-count___CPS__19334497\" class=\"gvl3-icon gvl3-icon-comment comment-count\"></span></p>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t<li class=\"no-image\">\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\" feature-header\">\r\n\t<a class=\"story\" rel=\"published-1347637703560\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/ethics/guide/\">Ethics guide</a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</h3>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Debates surrounding ethical issues in everyday life \t\r\n\t\t\t\t  <span id=\"dna-comment-count___CPS__